OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780315873
OL,3,CSkubala appointed as Bristol City boss
OL,5,FBristol City have confirmed the
OL,6,Fappointment of Lincoln boss Michael
OL,7,FSkubala as their new manager.
OL,9,FThe 43-year-old has signed a three-
OL,10,Fyear contract and succeeds former
OL,11,FEngland boss Roy Hodgson, who was put
OL,12,Fin caretaker charge of the club after
OL,13,Fhead coach Gerhard Struber was sacked.
OL,15,FSkubala won the League Managers'
OL,16,FAssociation League One manager of the
OL,17,Fseason after guiding Lincoln City to
OL,18,Fthe second tier for the first time in
OL,19,F65 years by winning the title.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
