PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780315873
OL,3,CSkubala appointed as Bristol City boss
OL,5,FSkubala said he's "ready for the
OL,6,Fchallenge ahead."
OL,8,F"I'm delighted to take up this
OL,9,Fexciting opportunity," he said.
OL,11,F"I'm looking forward to meeting the
OL,12,Fplayers, staff and supporters.
OL,13,FPreparations for pre-season are well
OL,14,Funderway and we have an important and
OL,15,Fexciting few months ahead."
OL,17,FBefore joining Lincoln City, Skubala
OL,18,Fled Leeds United's Under-21s as Head
OL,19,FCoach before moving to the first team
OL,20,Fstaff in the Premier League.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
