FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780315873
OL,3,CSkubala appointed as Bristol City boss
OL,5,FHe aslo briefly serving as Interim
OL,6,FHead Coach for the Whites' first team,
OL,7,Ftaking charge of three Premier League
OL,8,Fgames.
OL,10,FBristol City CEO, Charlie Boss, said:
OL,11,F"We are delighted that Michael has
OL,12,Fagreed to be our new manager.
OL,14,F"Michael's leadership qualities stood
OL,15,Fout through the interview process and
OL,16,Fwere clearly evident during a title-
OL,17,Fwinning season with Lincoln City. We
OL,18,Fare excited about what he will bring
OL,19,Fto Bristol City."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
