FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1780315873
OL,3,CSkubala appointed as Bristol City boss
OL,5,FHe added: "I want to thank City fans
OL,6,Ffor their support as we completed our
OL,7,Fsearch for the right person to lead
OL,8,Four First Team and I know they will
OL,9,Fjoin me in giving Michael the warmest
OL,10,Fof welcomes to the West Country."
OL,12,FJames Ellis said: "We have appointed
OL,13,Fsomeone who is highly regarded as a
OL,14,Fyoung British manager with a track
OL,15,Frecord of improving individual, team
OL,16,Fand club performance over a short
OL,17,Fperiod of time, leading to an
OL,18,Foutstanding promotion campaign with
OL,19,FLincoln City".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
